### Trouble Ticket Notes (noria:TroubleTicketNote) ###

<https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticketnote/TT20240423-001-Note1>
    a noria:TroubleTicketNote ;
    rdfs:label "Initial Diagnosis for TT20240423-001"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Initial diagnosis: Interface GE0/0/1 on CR01 is administratively up but operationally down. No local physical fault detected. Suspect external fiber issue."@en ;
