### Operation Plans (noria:OperationPlan) ###

<https://w3id.org/noria/operationplan/RestartWebServerService>
    a noria:OperationPlan ;
    rdfs:label "Restart Web Server Service Procedure"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Standard operating procedure to restart the web server service in case of high CPU or performance issues."@en ;
    skos:example "Steps: 1. Check logs for root cause. 2. Attempt graceful restart. 3. Force restart if necessary. 4. Monitor service availability."@en ;
    noria:operationPlanPreCondition <https://w3id.org/noria/actionprecondition/WebServerHighCPU> ;
    noria:operationPlanPostCondition <https://w3id.org/noria/actionpostcondition/WebServerServiceRestored> .

### Action Pre/Post Conditions (noria:ActionPreCondition, noria:ActionPostCondition) ###

<https://w3id.org/noria/actionprecondition/WebServerHighCPU>
    a noria:ActionPreCondition ;
    rdfs:label "Web Server High CPU Pre-Condition"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Condition: CPU utilization on web server exceeds 80% for more than 5 minutes."@en .

<https://w3id.org/noria/actionpostcondition/WebServerServiceRestored>
    a noria:ActionPostCondition ;
    rdfs:label "Web Server Service Restored Post-Condition"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Outcome: Web server service is accessible, and CPU utilization is below 50%."@en .

